OL,3,CWoman admits charges in connection
OL,4,Cwith deaths of four paddleboarders
OL,6,FA woman who organised a paddleboarding
OL,7,Fday out in Pembrokeshire has admitted
OL,8,Fthe gross negligence manslaughter of
OL,9,Ffour paddleboarders who died on the
OL,10,Ftrip.
OL,12,FPaul O'Dwyer, 42, Andrea Powell, 41,
OL,13,FMorgan Rogers, 24, and Nicola
OL,14,FWheatley, 40, all died following on
OL,15,Fthe tour in Haverfordwest Town Weir on
OL,16,F30 October 2021.
