OL,3,CWoman admits charges in connection
OL,4,Cwith deaths of four paddleboarders
OL,6,FThe four victims were part of a Stand
OL,7,FUp Paddle (SUP) paddleboarding tour `
OL,8,Forganised by Salty Dog Co Ltd which
OL,9,Fwas owned by Nerys Lloyd, 39, from
OL,10,FAberavon.
OL,12,FOn the day of the trip, there had been
OL,13,Fextensive flooding and weather
OL,14,Fwarnings were in force due to the fast
OL,15,Fflowing river.
OL,17,FAs the group approached the weir, the
OL,18,Fthree participants were pulled over
OL,19,Fthe top into its base and became
OL,20,Ftrapped.
