OL,3,CWoman admits charges in connection
OL,4,Cwith deaths of four paddleboarders
OL,6,FLloyd was present as an instructor on
OL,7,Fthe day of the tragedy alongside
OL,8,Ffellow instructor Mr O'Dwyer.
OL,10,FMr O'Dwyer, who initially exited the
OL,11,Friver safely, re-entered the water in
OL,12,Fan attempt to rescue the others but
OL,13,Fwas immediately dragged over the top.
OL,15,FThe four victims died as a result of
OL,16,Fdrowning/immersion.
