OL,3,CWoman admits charges in connection
OL,4,Cwith deaths of four paddleboarders
OL,6,FAn expert concluded that the tour
OL,7,Fshould not have taken place while
OL,8,Fencompassing the weir and that Lloyd
OL,9,Fdid not have a suitable qualification,
OL,10,Fand her planning and supervision was
OL,11,Finadequate.
OL,13,FLloyd who appeared in the dock wearing
OL,14,Fa blue shirt, dark trousers and using
OL,15,Fcrutches, also pleaded guilty to a
OL,16,FHealth and Safety at Work Act offence
OL,17,Fat Swansea Crown Court today.
OL,19,FLisa Rose, Specialist Prosecutor with
OL,20,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service Special
OL,21,FCrime Division, said:
