OL,3,CWoman admits charges in connection
OL,4,Cwith deaths of four paddleboarders
OL,6,F"This was an avoidable tragedy.
OL,7,FDespite going to check the state of
OL,8,Fthe river before departing on the
OL,9,Ftour, Nerys Lloyd failed to inspect
OL,10,Fthe weir.
OL,12,F"The majority of participants had
OL,13,Flimited experience, and Lloyd was not
OL,14,Fqualified to take paddleboarders out
OL,15,Fin such hazardous conditions.
