OL,3,CWoman admits charges in connection
OL,4,Cwith deaths of four paddleboarders
OL,6,F"There was no safety briefing or
OL,7,Fformal risk assessments, and the
OL,8,Fparticipants were not advised that
OL,9,Fthey would be traversing a weir or
OL,10,Finstructed on options to get out of
OL,11,Fthe water.
OL,13,F"Final decisions to continue with the
OL,14,Fevent were Lloyd's decision, and as a
OL,15,Fresult she held complete and entire
OL,16,Fresponsibility.
